        <%= link_to register_path, class: "btn btn-large btn-success" do %>
          <strong>Register Now</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;
          ( $20 &ndash; $50 )
        <% end %>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="span3">
            <h4>High End Ticket</h4>
            <p>This ticket price gets you nothing special extra, but it helps support the event so that some people (who otherwise can't afford the higher ticket price) can come for the lower price.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="span3">
